{"tid":2428893,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"何文田新開18challengkarting","createTime":"2021-03-02T01:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T04:43:48.000Z","uid":358801,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9703d2adc229bd030b10918ba6641a403896952","tid":2428893,"uid":358801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"好少開post經巴打提點重post，如果想睇好難明既論文襟下面link就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港終於有一個世界級小型賽車場 (長文慎入)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2427113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2427113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nExecutive Summary:<br />\n<br />\n控制室隨意調較架車快慢，你玩得越多次課得越多金就較得越快俾你令到自己以為有進步快咗再玩落去<br />\n<br />\n三歲細路仔就呃到姐，快撚啲執柒咗佢唔好影衰香港賽車同小型賽車行業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyJcS3m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdyJcS3m.png&h=9d201106&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78VyCu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78VyCu3.png&h=299091cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d58dbb721326981656f689090466bd99aed22ada","tid":2428893,"uid":78517,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"你知唔知試業個陣開full speed，撞到仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉兩個灣又要去執車<br />\n你估個個好似你冼拿上身咩<br />\n要拎個balance，適合返大部分人去玩架麻"},{"pid":"28d33e9a95bc96408851a5d0c2faa91e271c0b2b","tid":2428893,"uid":59715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T03:09:47.000Z","msg":"啲車行電就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8012557971077325a8f651f4a70bcbae8e4f1aa6","tid":2428893,"uid":233593,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"唔係幾同意玩得越多次課得越多金就較得越快呢個說法，我相信如果玩得越多次但係咁炒車應該都唔會較快啲俾你，控制車速馬力就係要做呢個角色。<br />\n可以話佢無講明會較慢係營商手法唔理想，唔可以講到俾多啲錢就會快啲<br />\n伸利：未玩過也沒興趣"},{"pid":"b2ea597c47a328df6093c6df4